{"tid":286950,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"「電腦白痴求打救」電腦開機冇b一聲 mon唔著","createTime":"2017-06-17T04:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T15:54:01.000Z","uid":12751,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23c8e009a2d54ff0e686b3afc9e2e5b5d9668a8d","tid":286950,"uid":12751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"琴晚開機已經係咁<br />\n開電腦果聲部機冇嗶一聲<br />\n個mon黑mon冇反應<br />\n已經試過重新插番ram同顯卡 情況都係一樣<br />\n亦試過唔插ram同顯卡就咁開 都係冇嗶一聲<br />\n有冇連登仔可以救救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afadd2d767e87511c325e5d20a0d006349f9e362","tid":286950,"uid":12751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:09:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493ea246f727fe10799443bfd0c2e790a477af32","tid":286950,"uid":12751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:24:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0203f5538e5876cbdcee40f37b3c47bf5f59b982","tid":286950,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"係完全無聲定點?<br />\n有無開扇聲？"},{"pid":"0bda47a542498d8d13014d6c11d93c774c1d8d86","tid":286950,"uid":12751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係完全無聲定點?<br />\n有無開扇聲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n風扇有郁<br />\n<br />\n但係平時開機都會有嗶一聲<br />\n依家冇埋嗶一樣<br />\nmon又冇反應"},{"pid":"146e29f8a0d90f1fcadab515b7a20a3dcc54f61e","tid":286950,"uid":12751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e88909c1